milestones.description: Gary Kirsten and Gibbs's 235-run partnership is SA's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 190 between Gary Kirsten and Mike Rindel
This is the highest match aggregate (603) involving teams South Africa & India in ODIs
Gary Kirsten and Gibbs's 235-run partnership is SA's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 232 between Cullinan and Jonty Rhodes

stories.title: India win amid scenes of low farce
stories.summary:
India won the first ODI against South Africa in a grandstand finish at
Kochi's Nehru stadium which ended in a grotesque manner after the teams
had walked off thinking the match was over and had to be called back to
complete it a second time
